<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="lv">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Rēķins {{ invoice_number }}</title>
    <style>
        @font-face {
            font-family: 'Instrument Sans';
            font-style: normal;
            font-weight: 400;
            font-display: swap;
            src: url('fonts/instrument-sans-latin-ext-400-normal.woff2') format('woff2');
            unicode-range: U+0100-02BA,U+02BD-02C5,U+02C7-02CC,U+02CE-02D7,U+02DD-02FF,U+0304,U+0308,U+0329,U+1D00-1DBF,U+1E00-1E9F,U+1EF2-1EFF,U+2020,U+20A0-20AB,U+20AD-20C0,U+2113,U+2C60-2C7F,U+A720-A7FF;
        }
        @font-face {
            font-family: 'Instrument Sans';
            font-style: normal;
            font-weight: 400;
            font-display: swap;
            src: url('fonts/instrument-sans-latin-400-normal.woff2') format('woff2');
            unicode-range: U+0000-00FF,U+0131,U+0152-0153,U+02BB-02BC,U+02C6,U+02DA,U+02DC,U+0304,U+0308,U+0329,U+2000-206F,U+20AC,U+2122,U+2191,U+2193,U+2212,U+2215,U+FEFF,U+FFFD;
        }
        @font-face {
            font-family: 'Instrument Sans';
            font-style: normal;
            font-weight: 500;
            font-display: swap;
            src: url('fonts/instrument-sans-latin-ext-500-normal.woff2') format('woff2');
            unicode-range: U+0100-02BA,U+02BD-02C5,U+02C7-02CC,U+02CE-02D7,U+02DD-02FF,U+0304,U+0308,U+0329,U+1D00-1DBF,U+1E00-1E9F,U+1EF2-1EFF,U+2020,U+20A0-20AB,U+20AD-20C0,U+2113,U+2C60-2C7F,U+A720-A7FF;
        }
        @font-face {
            font-family: 'Instrument Sans';
            font-style: normal;
            font-weight: 500;
            font-display: swap;
            src: url('fonts/instrument-sans-latin-500-normal.woff2') format('woff2');
            unicode-range: U+0000-00FF,U+0131,U+0152-0153,U+02BB-02BC,U+02C6,U+02DA,U+02DC,U+0304,U+0308,U+0329,U+2000-206F,U+20AC,U+2122,U+2191,U+2193,U+2212,U+2215,U+FEFF,U+FFFD;
        }
        @font-face {
            font-family: 'Instrument Sans';
            font-style: normal;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-display: swap;
            src: url('fonts/instrument-sans-latin-ext-600-normal.woff2') format('woff2');
            unicode-range: U+0100-02BA,U+02BD-02C5,U+02C7-02CC,U+02CE-02D7,U+02DD-02FF,U+0304,U+0308,U+0329,U+1D00-1DBF,U+1E00-1E9F,U+1EF2-1EFF,U+2020,U+20A0-20AB,U+20AD-20C0,U+2113,U+2C60-2C7F,U+A720-A7FF;
        }
        @font-face {
            font-family: 'Instrument Sans';
            font-style: normal;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-display: swap;
            src: url('fonts/instrument-sans-latin-600-normal.woff2') format('woff2');
            unicode-range: U+0000-00FF,U+0131,U+0152-0153,U+02BB-02BC,U+02C6,U+02DA,U+02DC,U+0304,U+0308,U+0329,U+2000-206F,U+20AC,U+2122,U+2191,U+2193,U+2212,U+2215,U+FEFF,U+FFFD;
        }
        @font-face {
            font-family: 'Inter';
            font-style: normal;
            font-weight: 400;
            font-display: swap;
            src: url('fonts/inter-latin-ext-400-normal.woff2') format('woff2');
            unicode-range: U+0100-02BA,U+02BD-02C5,U+02C7-02CC,U+02CE-02D7,U+02DD-02FF,U+0304,U+0308,U+0329,U+1D00-1DBF,U+1E00-1E9F,U+1EF2-1EFF,U+2020,U+20A0-20AB,U+20AD-20C0,U+2113,U+2C60-2C7F,U+A720-A7FF;
        }
        @font-face {
            font-family: 'Inter';
            font-style: normal;
            font-weight: 400;
            font-display: swap;
            src: url('fonts/inter-latin-400-normal.woff2') format('woff2');
            unicode-range: U+0000-00FF,U+0131,U+0152-0153,U+02BB-02BC,U+02C6,U+02DA,U+02DC,U+0304,U+0308,U+0329,U+2000-206F,U+20AC,U+2122,U+2191,U+2193,U+2212,U+2215,U+FEFF,U+FFFD;
        }

        @page { size: A4; margin: 0; }
        * { box-sizing: border-box; }
        html, body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            width: 595px;
            height: 842px;
            font-family: 'Instrument Sans', ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif;
            background: #FFFFFF;
            color: #000;
        }

        .page {
            position: relative;
            width: 595px;
            height: 842px;
            background: #FFFFFF;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        /* --- Header (fixed anchors) --- */
        .hdr-title {
            position: absolute;
            left: 33px;
            top: 33px;
            font-family: 'Instrument Sans', sans-serif;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 18.2439px;
            line-height: 22px;
            color: #000;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .hdr-meta {
            position: absolute;
            top: 33px;
        }
        .hdr-meta--1 { left: 125px; width: 87px; }
        .hdr-meta--2 { left: 240px; width: 81.53px; }

        .hdr-meta .hdr-lbl {
            font-weight: 400;
            font-size: 7px;
            line-height: 9px;
            color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .hdr-meta .hdr-val {
            font-weight: 500;
            font-size: 9px;
            line-height: 11px;
            color: #000;
            margin: 0;
            margin-top: 2px;
            padding: 0;
            word-wrap: break-word;
        }

        .hdr-logo {
            position: absolute;
            left: 450px;
            top: 34.78px;
            width: 112.32px;
            height: 15.97px;
        }
        .hdr-logo img {
            display: block;
            width: 112.32px;
            height: 15.97px;
            object-fit: contain;
            object-position: left center;
        }

        .page-divider--top {
            position: absolute;
            left: 32.5px;
            top: 63px;
            width: 530px;
            height: 0.5px;
            background: #CCCCCC;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            border: 0;
            outline: none;
        }

        /* --- Main column --- */
        .main-column {
            position: absolute;
            left: 48px;
            top: 120px;
            width: 500px;
        }

        .main-stack {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 46px;
            width: 500px;
        }

        /* Section titles (party + inline sections) */
        .sec-title-plain {
            height: 11px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 9px;
            line-height: 11px;
            color: #000;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .divider-240 {
            width: 240px;
            height: 0.47px;
            background: #CCCCCC;
            border: none;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }

        .divider-500 {
            width: 500px;
            height: 0.5px;
            background: #CCCCCC;
            border: none;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }

        /* Field typography */
        .fld-lbl {
            font-weight: 400;
            font-size: 6.84145px;
            line-height: 8px;
            color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .fld-val {
            font-weight: 500;
            font-size: 9.12193px;
            line-height: 11px;
            color: #000;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .fld-lbl + .fld-val { margin-top: 2.28px; }

        /* --- 5) Parties --- */
        .parties-row {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: row;
            gap: 20px;
            width: 500px;
        }

        .party-col {
            width: 240px;
            flex: 0 0 240px;
            min-width: 0;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: flex-start;
            gap: 0;
        }

        .party-col .sec-title-plain { margin-bottom: 0; }
        .party-col .divider-240 { margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0; }

        .party-body {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 11.33px;
            width: 240px;
            margin-top: 0;
        }

        .pair-row-25 {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: row;
            gap: 25.09px;
            width: 100%;
        }
        .pair-row-25 .pair-cell {
            flex: 1;
            min-width: 0;
        }

        /* --- 6) Route + map row --- */
        .route-map-row {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: row;
            align-items: flex-start;
            gap: 20px;
            width: 500px;
            min-height: 118.51px;
        }

        .route-col {
            width: 240px;
            flex: 0 0 240px;
            min-width: 0;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
        }

        .route-sec-head {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: row;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 4.56px;
            height: 23.84px;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .route-sec-head .route-sec-title {
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 9px;
            line-height: 11px;
            color: #000;
        }

        .bubble-route {
            width: 23.84px;
            height: 23.84px;
            min-width: 23.84px;
            min-height: 23.84px;
            border-radius: 11.9207px;
            background: #D7FF01;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 4.77px;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        .bubble-route img {
            width: 13.11px;
            height: 13.11px;
            display: block;
            object-fit: contain;
        }

        .route-col .divider-240 {
            margin-top: 0;
            margin-bottom: 0;
            height: 0.5px;
        }

        .route-flow {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: row;
            align-items: flex-start;
            gap: 9.12px;
            margin-top: 4px;
            flex: 1;
            min-height: 0;
        }

        .route-rail {
            width: 9.12px;
            height: 51.31px;
            flex-shrink: 0;
            display: block;
            object-fit: fill;
        }

        .route-text-col {
            flex: 1;
            min-width: 0;
            padding-left: 0;
        }

        .route-stop + .route-stop {
            margin-top: 8px;
        }

        .route-stop .route-lbl {
            font-weight: 400;
            font-size: 6.84145px;
            line-height: 8px;
            color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .route-stop .route-val {
            font-weight: 500;
            font-size: 9.12193px;
            line-height: 11px;
            color: #000;
            margin: 0;
            margin-top: 2.28px;
            padding: 0;
            word-wrap: break-word;
        }

        .route-inner-rule {
            width: 100%;
            height: 0.47px;
            background: #CCCCCC;
            border: none;
            margin: 6px 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .route-bottom-rule {
            width: 240px;
            height: 0.5px;
            background: #CCCCCC;
            border: none;
            margin: 6px 0 0 0;
            padding: 0;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }

        .map-box {
            width: 240px;
            height: 118px;
            flex: 0 0 240px;
            border-radius: 7.98169px;
            overflow: hidden;
            background: #e8e8e8;
            position: relative;
        }

        .map-box-inner {
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            top: 0;
            right: 0;
            bottom: 0;
        }

        .map-box-inner .map-tile-img {
            position: absolute;
            display: block;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            border: 0;
        }
        .map-box-inner img.map-fill {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            object-fit: cover;
            object-position: center;
            display: block;
        }

        .map-route-svg {
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            top: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            z-index: 1;
            pointer-events: none;
        }

        .map-pin {
            position: absolute;
            width: 8px;
            height: 8px;
            box-sizing: content-box;
            border: 1.5px solid #000000;
            border-radius: 50%;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
            z-index: 2;
            pointer-events: none;
        }
        .map-pin-pickup { background: #ffffff; }
        .map-pin-drop { background: #DEDEDE; }

        /* --- 7) Service + pricing (inside block 2) --- */
        .route-service-block {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 9px;
            width: 500px;
        }

        .service-stack {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 9px;
            width: 500px;
            min-height: 70.34px;
        }

        .service-top-row {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: row;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            width: 500px;
            height: 22.56px;
        }

        .svc-left-group {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: row;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 4.56px;
            width: 261.12px;
            flex: 0 0 261.12px;
        }

        .bubble-svc {
            width: 22.56px;
            height: 22.56px;
            min-width: 22.56px;
            min-height: 22.56px;
            border-radius: 11.28px;
            background: #D7FF01;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        .bubble-svc img {
            width: 11.28px;
            height: 11.28px;
            display: block;
            object-fit: contain;
        }

        .svc-left-group .svc-title-txt {
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 9px;
            line-height: 11px;
            color: #000;
        }

        .svc-date-txt {
            width: 207px;
            flex: 0 0 207px;
            text-align: right;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 9px;
            line-height: 11px;
            color: #000;
        }

        .price-row {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(6, 1fr);
            width: 500px;
            min-height: 29.28px;
            align-items: start;
            column-gap: 4px;
        }

        .price-col .p-lbl {
            font-weight: 400;
            font-size: 6.84145px;
            line-height: 8px;
            color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            white-space: normal;
        }
        .price-col .p-val {
            font-weight: 500;
            font-size: 9.12193px;
            line-height: 11px;
            color: #000;
            margin: 0;
            margin-top: 4px;
            padding: 0;
            white-space: nowrap;
        }

        .price-col--last {
            text-align: right;
        }
        .price-col--last .p-lbl { text-align: right; }
        .price-col--last .p-val {
            font-weight: 600;
            text-align: right;
        }

        /* --- 8) Payment --- */
        .pay-block {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 0;
            width: 500px;
            margin-top: 0;
        }

        .pay-head {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: row;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 4.56px;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .bubble-pay {
            width: 22.8px;
            height: 22.8px;
            min-width: 22.8px;
            min-height: 22.8px;
            border-radius: 11.4px;
            background: #D7FF01;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 4.56px;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        .bubble-pay img {
            width: 9px;
            height: 9px;
            display: block;
            object-fit: contain;
        }

        .pay-head .pay-title-txt {
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 9px;
            line-height: 11px;
            color: #000;
        }

        .pay-block .divider-500 {
            margin-top: 6px;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .pay-row-spec {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: row;
            gap: 59px;
            width: 289px;
            min-height: 21.28px;
        }
        .pay-row-spec .pay-cell {
            flex: 1;
            min-width: 0;
        }

        .legal-lines {
            margin-top: 10px;
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            font-weight: 400;
            font-size: 6px;
            line-height: 9px;
            color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
        }
        .legal-lines p {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .legal-lines p + p {
            margin-top: 2px;
        }

        /* --- 9) Footer --- */
        .footer-legal {
            position: absolute;
            left: 32.5px;
            top: 796px;
            width: 530px;
            height: 24.5px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 10px;
        }

        .footer-legal .footer-rule {
            width: 530px;
            height: 0.5px;
            background: #CCCCCC;
            border: none;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }

        .footer-legal .footer-row {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: row;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: flex-start;
            height: 14px;
            gap: 12px;
        }

        .footer-left-g {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: row;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 6px;
            max-width: 48%;
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            font-size: 6px;
            line-height: 7px;
            font-weight: 400;
            color: rgba(34, 32, 31, 0.35);
        }
        .footer-left-g img {
            height: 10px;
            width: auto;
            display: block;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }

        .footer-right-g {
            max-width: 52%;
            text-align: right;
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            font-size: 6px;
            line-height: 7px;
            font-weight: 400;
            color: rgba(34, 32, 31, 0.35);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="page">
    <h1 class="hdr-title">Rēķins</h1>

    <div class="hdr-meta hdr-meta--1">
        <div class="hdr-lbl">Rēķina Nr / Pasūtījuma Nr</div>
        <div class="hdr-val">{{ invoice_number }}</div>
    </div>
    <div class="hdr-meta hdr-meta--2">
        <div class="hdr-lbl">Rēķina datums:</div>
        <div class="hdr-val">{{ issue_date }}</div>
    </div>

    <div class="hdr-logo">
        <img src="invoice-assets/group-1122.svg" width="112" height="16" alt="hevvi" style="width:112.32px;height:15.97px;">
    </div>

    <hr class="page-divider--top" />

    <div class="main-column">
        <div class="main-stack">
            {# 1) Supplier / customer #}
            <section class="parties-row">
                <div class="party-col">
                    <div class="sec-title-plain">Pakalpojuma sniedzējs</div>
                    <hr class="divider-240" />
                    <div class="party-body">
                        <div class="field">
                            <div class="fld-lbl">Pārdevējs (Pakalpojuma sniedzējs):</div>
                            <div class="fld-val">{{ seller_name }}</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="pair-row-25">
                            <div class="pair-cell">
                                <div class="fld-lbl">Reģ. Nr.</div>
                                <div class="fld-val">{{ seller_reg }}</div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="pair-cell">
                                <div class="fld-lbl">PVN reģ. Nr.</div>
                                <div class="fld-val">{{ seller_vat }}</div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="field">
                            <div class="fld-lbl">Juridiskā adrese:</div>
                            <div class="fld-val">{{ seller_line1 }}</div>
                            {% if seller_line2 %}<div class="fld-val" style="margin-top: 4px;">{{ seller_line2 }}</div>{% endif %}
                        </div>
                        <div class="pair-row-25">
                            <div class="pair-cell">
                                <div class="fld-lbl">E-pasts:</div>
                                <div class="fld-val">{{ seller_email }}</div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="pair-cell">
                                <div class="fld-lbl">Tālrunis:</div>
                                <div class="fld-val">{{ seller_phone }}</div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="party-col">
                    <div class="sec-title-plain">Pakalpojumu saņēmējs</div>
                    <hr class="divider-240" />
                    <div class="party-body">
                        <div class="field">
                            <div class="fld-lbl">Pircējs (Klients):</div>
                            <div class="fld-val">{{ buyer_company }}</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="pair-row-25">
                            <div class="pair-cell">
                                <div class="fld-lbl">Reģ. Nr.</div>
                                <div class="fld-val">{{ buyer_reg }}</div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="pair-cell">
                                <div class="fld-lbl">PVN reģ. Nr.</div>
                                <div class="fld-val">{{ buyer_vat }}</div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="field">
                            <div class="fld-lbl">Adrese:</div>
                            {% for line in buyer_address_lines %}
                                <div class="fld-val"{% if not loop.first %} style="margin-top: 4px;"{% endif %}>{{ line }}</div>
                            {% endfor %}
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            {# 2) Route + map + service + pricing #}
            <section class="route-service-block">
                <div class="route-map-row">
                    <div class="route-col">
                        <div class="route-sec-head">
                            <span class="bubble-route" aria-hidden="true"><img src="invoice-assets/fi-446075.svg" alt=""></span>
                            <span class="route-sec-title">Maršruts</span>
                        </div>
                        <hr class="divider-240" />
                        <div class="route-flow">
                            <img src="invoice-assets/group-1059.svg" class="route-rail" width="9.12" height="51.31" alt="">
                            <div class="route-text-col">
                                <div class="route-stop">
                                    <div class="route-lbl">Pickup</div>
                                    <div class="route-val">{{ pickup }}</div>
                                </div>
                                <hr class="route-inner-rule" />
                                <div class="route-stop">
                                    <div class="route-lbl">Delivery</div>
                                    <div class="route-val">{{ delivery }}</div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <hr class="route-bottom-rule" />
                    </div>
                    <div class="map-box">
                        <div class="map-box-inner">
                            {% if map_show_pins and map_inner_w and map_inner_h and map_img_w %}
                                <img class="map-tile-img" src="{{ map_data_uri|raw }}" alt=""
                                     style="left: {{ map_img_left }}px; top: {{ map_img_top }}px; width: {{ map_img_w }}px; height: {{ map_img_h }}px;">
                            {% else %}
                                <img class="map-fill" src="{{ map_data_uri|raw }}" alt="">
                            {% endif %}
                            {% if map_show_pins and map_inner_w and map_inner_h %}
                                <svg class="map-route-svg" viewBox="0 0 {{ map_inner_w }} {{ map_inner_h }}" preserveAspectRatio="none" aria-hidden="true">
                                    <line x1="{{ map_pickup_left }}" y1="{{ map_pickup_top }}" x2="{{ map_drop_left }}" y2="{{ map_drop_top }}"
                                          stroke="#000000" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
                                </svg>
                                <span class="map-pin map-pin-pickup" style="left: {{ map_pickup_left }}px; top: {{ map_pickup_top }}px;"></span>
                                <span class="map-pin map-pin-drop" style="left: {{ map_drop_left }}px; top: {{ map_drop_top }}px;"></span>
                            {% endif %}
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="service-stack">
                    <div class="service-top-row">
                        <div class="svc-left-group">
                            <span class="bubble-svc" aria-hidden="true"><img src="invoice-assets/delivered-1.svg" alt=""></span>
                            <span class="svc-title-txt">Pakalpojums</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="svc-date-txt">Pakalpojuma sniegšanas datums: {{ service_date }}</div>
                    </div>
                    <hr class="divider-500" />
                    <div class="price-row">
                        <div class="price-col">
                            <div class="p-lbl">Kravas piegādes maksa</div>
                            <div class="p-val">{{ amount_freight }}</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="price-col">
                            <div class="p-lbl">Cena bez PVN</div>
                            <div class="p-val">{{ amount_cena_bez_pvn }}</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="price-col">
                            <div class="p-lbl">{{ commission_label }}</div>
                            <div class="p-val">{{ amount_commission }}</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="price-col">
                            <div class="p-lbl">Starpsumma (bez PVN)</div>
                            <div class="p-val">{{ amount_subtotal }}</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="price-col">
                            <div class="p-lbl">{{ vat_label }}</div>
                            <div class="p-val">{{ amount_vat }}</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="price-col price-col--last">
                            <div class="p-lbl">KOPĀ APMAKSAI (ar PVN)</div>
                            <div class="p-val">{{ amount_gross }}</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            {# 3) Payment #}
            <section class="pay-block">
                <div class="pay-head">
                    <span class="bubble-pay" aria-hidden="true"><img src="invoice-assets/fi-157977.svg" alt=""></span>
                    <span class="pay-title-txt">Maksājuma informācija</span>
                </div>
                <hr class="divider-500" />
                <div class="pay-row-spec">
                    <div class="pay-cell">
                        <div class="fld-lbl">Maksājuma veids:</div>
                        <div class="fld-val">{{ payment_method }}</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="pay-cell">
                        <div class="fld-lbl">Maksājuma statuss:</div>
                        <div class="fld-val">{{ payment_status }}</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="legal-lines">
                    <p>Rēķins sagatavots elektroniski un ir derīgs bez paraksta</p>
                    <p>PVN piemērots saskaņā ar Pievienotās vērtības nodokļa likumu</p>
                </div>
            </section>
        </div>
    </div>

    <footer class="footer-legal">
        <hr class="footer-rule" />
        <div class="footer-row">
            <div class="footer-left-g">
                <img src="invoice-assets/group-1123.svg" alt="" aria-hidden="true">
                <span>Pakalpojums sniegts caur Hevvi digitālo platformu</span>
            </div>
            <div class="footer-right-g">Hevvi App nodrošina digitālu platformu transporta pakalpojumu organizēšanai. Komisijas maksa tiek ieturēta par platformas izmantošanu un administrēšanu.</div>
        </div>
    </footer>
</div>
</body>
</html>
